room_title: Escape room "The Boss's Office" by Mass Exodus in Chicago
room_address: 9206 S Keating Ave Oak Lawn, IL 60453
room_description: Mr. O'Henry is the boss you love to hate and now he's been a no-show for two weeks. While any day without him is a good one, it's payday, and the direct deposits have not hit the bank. Search his office, figure out where he's gone, and find your hard-earned money. Will you succeed?
